text: Pasindu Madushan (born 21 November 1992) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Kalutara Town Club in the 2017–18 SLC Twenty20 Tournament on 24 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Kalutara Town Club cricketers Category:Nugegoda Sports Welfare Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
